    • getInstance

      protected Category getInstance​(CategoryType type, java.lang.String id)
      Construct and return the requested Category type. Dynamically binds to allow this method to be overridden in subclasses, to create custom instantiation while maintaining a constant order of operations.
      Parameters:
      type - The type of the category to create.
      id - The ID of the category to create.
      Returns:
      A new category with the given ID matching the given type. Should never return null.
